823
00:41:41,129 --> 00:41:43,864
♪ <i>Thinking that life has</i>
<i>passed them by</i> ♪

824
00:41:47,235 --> 00:41:50,214
♪ <i>Don't give up until you</i> ♪

825
00:41:50,238 --> 00:41:52,589
♪ <i>Drink from the silver cup</i> ♪

826
00:41:53,157 --> 00:41:56,510
♪ <i>And ride that highway in the sky</i> ♪

827
00:41:57,995 --> 00:42:02,641
♪ <i>Well, I'm on my way back home</i> ♪

